{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":586911,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":122077,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"赞同，谁也不愿做个恶人，可是凭什么好人就tm被枪指着？","timestamp":1605850250,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":586936,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":122077,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"说实话，你要是觉得全民人肉网暴影响小，那学弟被诬告也不可怜；你要是觉得人肉网暴影响很大，那dj罪不至此。","timestamp":1605850403,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":586956,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122077,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob：dj自己无理取闹在先，这波反噬她自己罢了。她不无辜，所以活该。学弟无辜，所以可怜。","timestamp":1605850553,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587019,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":122077,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 这就看她的错误和全网喷的惩罚到底哪边重了。我觉得她要是被清华学子喷，那太活该了。但现在微博多少人喷她，这后果有点重","timestamp":1605851063,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587062,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122077,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol：那么加上以后xsr受害者更难获取信任这一条呢？而且如果监控没有还学弟清白，那么今天面对这些的就可能是他。还到她身上不算过分吧。","timestamp":1605851399,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587068,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":122077,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"1/10","timestamp":1605851441,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587153,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":122077,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"同意Bob罪不至此，就像你小考作弊，让你退学通报批评","timestamp":1605852113,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587169,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":122077,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re : 赞同。想利用舆论却被反噬，只能说自取其辱","timestamp":1605852198,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587213,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permiss